  local table_separator="|---------|------|"
  local kicker="\n- 👑 Most Important Thing Today:\n- 1st 🐸 I'll eat:\n- 2nd 🐸 I'll eat:\n- 3rd 🐸 I'll eat:\n\n"

  ###### Day of week should include 📅 and weeknum on Mondays
